ibly high bar for who we bring into UBS.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">UBS executives fear they are taking on a bank =
that has traditionally been much more willing to accept risky clients and o=
ffer them high-stakes products. Credit Suisse=E2=80=99s final few years as =
an independent company were marked by a series of scandals and crises, whic=
