uding any =E2=80=9Cnote, stock, ... bond, debenture, evidence of indebtedne=
ss, certificate of interest or participation in any profit-sharing agreemen=
t, collateral-trust certificate, preorganization certificate or subscriptio=
n, transferable share [or]=C2=A0investment contract,=E2=80=9D=C2=A0are secu=
rities. =E2=80=9CInvestment contract=E2=80=9D=C2=A0is the vaguest of those =
terms, so when the SEC argues that something weird and novel is a security,=
 it usually argues that it=E2=80=99s an investment contract. And the Howey =
test says that an investment contract is =E2=80=9Can investment of money in=
