th Koreans access to the engineer=E2=80=99s computer and allowed hackers to=
 break into Sky Mavis. Ultimately they stole more than $600 million=E2=80=
=94mostly from players of Sky Mavis=E2=80=99s digital pets game, Axie Infin=
ity.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It was the country=E2=80=99s biggest haul in f=
ive years of digital heists that have netted more than $3 billion for the N=
orth Koreans, according to the blockchain analytics firm Chainalysis.=C2=A0=
That money is being used to fund about 50% of North Korea=E2=80=99s ballist=
ic missile program, U.S. officials say, which has been developed in tandem =
with its nuclear weapons.</p>
